-- Ver.di Welcomes RWE’s Sale of Stake in Saarland’s VSE Utility
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-22T11:05:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-22/ver-di-welcomes-rwe-s-sale-of-stake-in-saarland-s-vse-utility.html
Germany ’s Ver.di labor union
welcomed a plan by  RWE AG (RWE)  to sell part of its stake in Saarland
utility VSE AG to municipalities in the region.  Ver.di assumes that its demands, including keeping jobs in
Saarland and safeguarding VSE’s independence, will be met by the
agreement to sell 19 percent of the company to municipalities,
it said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
